name: The Final Domestic Delta 747 Flight
description:
In full disclosure, I'm a huge Delta Air Lines fan.

Earlier this week, I participated in an amazing celebration to "retire" Delta's N669US on the final domestic run for a Delta 747. Join me for this incredible (and sad) journey from LAX to DTW.

Check out SpeedbirdHD's channel. It's awesome! 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCP0SSw5k85FzNjvGXIS6NAQ
